All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
@Entity
public class Branch
extends AuditModel
Object-oriented representation for table branches

Storages: Possible transfers to another branch of the history, when user came to fork

Logic: When user came to the fork, game checks all available branches with their limitations and takes suitable.
